title: Big Booty Judy, Ratchet Memorial, Family Phewd, Ready to Love and more.
itunes:title: Big Booty Judy, Ratchet Memorial, Family Phewd, Ready to Love and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! He got another aka and it's proof that cool has no expiration date. Someone writing to The CLO is being hella petty. Nothing but choices and broken promises in BK. Get Ready to Love Tommy's curveballs because it's goin' down in the DMV! Our favorite Gentleman of Leisure got something just for you. Fool #2 brings us Ratchet Memorial. Is Thomas Miles jelly of Steve or nah? Popeye's turns the heat up with one of the baddest! Today in Closing Remarks, Steve warns us about bringing tomorrow's problems into our day.
